[SN]TITLE[SN]
Euro 2016 warm-ups: Wales players' attitude pleases Chris Coleman

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Chris Coleman says he was pleased with under-strength Wales' "performance and attitude" despite a 1-0 defeat in their Euro 2016 warm-up in Ukraine.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is not supported on this device
Wales' Easter double-headers against Northern Ireland and Ukraine were the final games before Coleman names his 23-man Euro 2016 squad.
